 article on why it should be important to maintain diplomatic relationships in Shadowbane. When they give you info to post, I don't just want the same press release that everyone else gets, I want to see an analysis of it: the good, the bad, and the interesting. <P>If you can do that, then you've got another subscriber.<P><P>/edit<P>&gt;(Let me spell this one out <BR>&gt;for the unenlightened... Suzy256 is <BR>&gt;an analogy for the many <BR>&gt;game's that sound perfect but <BR>&gt;end up being not so <BR>&gt;perfect) <P>Lol, thanks for clearing that one up. I really hope that nobody missed that analogy. <P><BR>Mortarion<BR><i>The god of death and decay</i>
